Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:11.63,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鸣海哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:16.28,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鸣海哥哥不在后 已经过了两个月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.36,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鸣海哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:32.37,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我… 我很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:40.34,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}话虽如此 因为当时的伤 住了很久的院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.49,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是今天 要久违的去上小学了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷 请戴围脖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.89,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白银现在退出了吸管马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.53,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在我家作为女仆生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.84,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说是因为我随时可能再次被袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:02.19,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想在我身边照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.83,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这份心意让我很高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快别这样 白银 我自己会吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.80,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但有点保护过度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 这身打扮是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今天起我也要陪少爷去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 白银今天起就是高中生了来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我借着才贺家的名字 顺利编入了高中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就在少爷学校隔壁 有什么事我会马上赶去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 可是不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想两人一起走着去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:04.54,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鸣海哥哥 我变得这么能笑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:09.09,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白银好漂亮 好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:14.43,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定是因为鸣海哥哥教了好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:18.48,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对我们 对我们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\i1}胜 你要笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\i1}有时会哭也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\i1}可是 要笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以说一句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很难开口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但我听说少爷在学校被欺负了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天起 请注意不要太引人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因为引人注意一事会让那些人来劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可是白银 我之前也没有做过什么引人注意的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,请看我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这个眼睛与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在马戏学校被各种欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,白银也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 那些家伙在我保持低调的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,也慢慢对我失去了兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那不是胜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,难得大驾光临啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的猎物复活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我去隔壁高中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗 无论如何都不要引人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是被人欺负的话 就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我会用丑角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗的艺术…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那样更引人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊 我被做了这种事来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么说来 在那个宅子里也没有鞋子来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和那时比起来 这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么回事 居然在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,先前明明马上就哭出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,才贺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,海外旅行好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,海外旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 我们听老师这样说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,才贺因为长期旅行要请假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对了 嗯 很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有钱真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,下次慢慢告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么海外旅行 看你还能装逼多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 本班迎来了留学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,体验和法国的文化差异
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对大家来说也是很好的学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:54.11,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1056,402)\b0\bord0\shad0\be2\c&H8E9A9A&}转\N校\N生\N\N才\N贺\N白\N银
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我是才贺白银 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,美爆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么 管你是什么法国佬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,装什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那么才贺同学坐最后一排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那个旅行箱是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你想什么呢 快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 你没有受伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是法国人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,搭个话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,法语的你好记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:59.26,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\b0\bord0\fs45\shad0\be2\c&HA9ABA6&\frz344.8\move(1671.2,370.8,1581.2,370.8)}小\N胜\N\N来\N换\N尿\N裤\N吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b0\bord0\fs45\shad0\be2\c&HA9ABA6&\frz22.45\move(329,886,239,886)}我\N给\N你\N100\N万\N帮\N我\N换\N吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,织江 梶山他们又开始欺负人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 虽然让人很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但才贺也有不对的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,总是那么懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我是班长 也不想帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,画的真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,起立 敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少爷果然在被人欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少爷 太可怜啦 这里就由我出马…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 这样太扎眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 梶山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不来学校 都不打个招呼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是我们的跑腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,少看不起人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就会撒娇的公子哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手 梶山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,才贺做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个孩子不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,织江 怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是喜欢胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,…才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那就闪一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小心我也拿你当小胜病菌的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 梶山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,上田同学也算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为你这样才会被欺负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你笑个什么鬼 小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这家伙变了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和先前不是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,才贺？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 因为不想吓到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才用头巾蒙着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 早晚会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为下节课是体育
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事 虽然没什么好宣传的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但我之所以请假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不是去旅游了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我遇到了很可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了世上还有人把杀人不当一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我当时受的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 和这个比起来 不论怎么受欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,梶山同学问我笑什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为 有个人救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人无论何时都没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,无论多么危险的时候都笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 为了成为他那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要保持笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思 才贺同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,听说她入学第一天就翘课了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在各种意义上都很引人注目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我说仲町先生 你也适可为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的房租已经拖欠一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再等一下下 我就一起都还清
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊 我劝你放弃什么马戏团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,已经落伍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说实在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里落伍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是别人拼上性命去做的事业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 才贺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:12:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊 刚才梶山那时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你说有人救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一个是法国女性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她在隔壁高中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,白银那么认真 高中生活应该应付得来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不必忆起空虚的喝彩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么一直留在耳畔 肩上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,且入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一抹丹青入镜来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 她真的是外国人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,声音好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 白银 不用太认真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:13:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我来试吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 白银同学在马戏团待过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那运动神经也很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那么请小冢同学示范
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小冢是体操部的 总想惹人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,惹人注意？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我也因为这个眼睛的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在马戏学校发生了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,白银同学待过马戏团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 也让白银同学示范一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我不想惹人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 不用勉强 能示范点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底要做什么才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是刚才的人做的那种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,装模作样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她能做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只是少见罢了 小冢才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那种玩意根本不是体操
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真是败给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 可是听才贺这么一说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那个白银真是完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 上田同学 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白银才不是完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白银无论自己被怎样夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无论多么受到喜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都绝不会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只会歪歪头 露出寂寞的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道白银的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是在机关宅邸里受伤 住院的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷 我当时没能对加藤露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,加藤明明被ZONAPHA病折磨着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,明明需要他人的笑容治愈他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当时 对于需要笑容的鸣海哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白银没能露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 只要白银一天没有忘记鸣海哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她就一天没法露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是 要忘记鸣海哥哥是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说 告诉我 鸣海哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要怎么做 才能让白银露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,才贺 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,白银下次要加入哪里的马戏团？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,马戏团？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 她原本就是团员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,再去加入就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想看白银表演的马戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊 马戏团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 为什么我要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为老爹惹怒了房东啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,至少要给扫除才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,话说接下来要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,果然像房东说的 马戏团已经落伍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 孩子们都沉迷于动画游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是老天爷不让我们演马戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等等少爷 要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是马戏团啊 马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,马戏团 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,记得就在这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 虽然我还没看过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但这个城市也有马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,白银喜欢马戏团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己的事情怎么样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,才不好 白银总是为了我做这做那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 白银也可以做自己喜欢的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 去加入马戏团就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,听你们说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这位小姐是想加入我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是仲町马戏团的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我是团长仲町信夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大美女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 我叫胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 请让白银加入马戏团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷 我还没说要加入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,加入吧 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小朋友 不要任性哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,马戏可不是光靠小朋友的任性就能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥们也是马戏团的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你们做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,既然被你问到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就没有办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,白银
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,白银也露一手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你真要来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷 我的使命是守护少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 如果你希望我做喜欢的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我就和这些人一起演马戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我一眼就能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你有艺人之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉有希望了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,仲町马戏团复活的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,重新介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是纪之和浩男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的驯兽师 Sister莉洁罗蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才要请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:37.47,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鸣海哥哥 我会微笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:38.79,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无时无刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.74,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为鸣海哥哥这样教过我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:45.51,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白银总有一天也会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:50.68,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 鸣海哥哥 放心吧
Comment: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================C-PART=================================================
Comment: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================ED=================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:19.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}舞い上がれマリオネット　美しく果て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:23.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}生きる価値　戦うしか私にはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:28.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}人を捨ててまで　この怒りは何故
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:34.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}君がいないと　もう笑うことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:40.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}悪いのは自分だと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:44.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}うまく笑えない　人形みたいだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:49.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誰かに操られているように　そんな気もして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:53.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}どうして生きてるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:57.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誰にもわかってもらえないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:03.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}思ってた痛みも　君が抱きしめてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:11.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}絡まる手足が解けてくみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.71,0:23:16.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}舞い上がれマリオネット　今なら届きそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:21.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}君と出会うまで私には何もなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:25.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}すべて賭けても　守りたいもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:32.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,400)}悲しい気持ちも　君が教えてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:19.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}起舞吧人偶 美丽的逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:23.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我生存的价值只有战斗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:28.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不惜舍弃做人 这份愤怒为何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:34.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}没有你在 我已经没法笑得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:40.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}本以为是自己不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:44.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就像不会笑的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:49.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}感觉像是被什么人操纵着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:53.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}为什么要活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:57.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}没有任何人理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:03.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}想到这里的那份心痛 都被你紧拥在怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:11.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}被束缚的手脚似乎解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.71,0:23:16.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}起舞吧人偶 现在感觉能送达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:21.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}和你相遇之前我一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:25.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使赌上一切 也要守护之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:32.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,400)}悲伤的感情 也是你教会了我
